												<div class="description author withsidebar">
													<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/sarahthornton/">Sarah Thornton</a></h6>
													Sarah Thornton is a sociologist and author of three critically acclaimed books, including the international bestseller <em>Seven Days in the Art World</em>. She was a scholar-in-residence at University of California, Berkeley, for three years while writing <em>Tits Up</em>. She lives in San Francisco, California.																									</div>
